---
title: Rosemary Pork Meatballs and Cheesy Chips with red wine jus and roasted carrots
description: A hint of something herby in this dish comes in the form of rosemary, which is mixed into the pork meatballs in this hearty recipe. Rosemary is a robust herb that pairs particularly well with pork, and it's not a poor accompaniment for the cheesy chips that also appear on this plate either.
